    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is. It requires significant mechanical attention, as the engine runs roughly and there is a noticeable leak in the transmission system. The exterior has substantial rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling extensively. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears and the air conditioning is currently non-functional. This would be a suitable project car or a source for parts for someone with the right tools and expertise.",
