      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example retains its high-revving character with crisp throttle response via individual throttle bodies and seamless double-VANOS operation. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels, managed by a factory M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains composed, benefiting from a documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed suspension bushings. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is robust, offering a visceral analog driving experience with an 8,000 RPM redline. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul.",
